divs: Sighting Detailslooking at eastern sky, very high up ,watched two points of light, one appeared to be the front of the object and the other the rear. these points of light stayed at the same distance from each other which was several miles apart and both moved at the same speed. traveled at a very high altitude. if these were two planes then they were traveling the exact same heading and at the exact same speed. never seen 2 planes do that at that altitude that close together. lights moved from north to south in perfect straight line to each other.
